es and a fever, witnesses toldLe Parisien.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three of them had marks on their arms and two men who were stopped at the scene were later released by police  Paris has launched a major security operation ahead of the opening ceremony, with armed guards seen patrolling the streets.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0663621409461146e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police want to avoid tourists being afraid as thousands flock to the French capital for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9680435348563349, \"rank\": 0.03282310930171358, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 45,000 police officers have been drafted in from 43 different countries, with UK sniffer dogs being sent to support the French authorities.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2487, \"end\": 2489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999998537587196, \"rank\": 6.983899995706405e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9680435348563349, \"rank\": 0.03282310930171358, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res